1.1
log
@Fix some security issues with gnats.

Some additional fixes from millert@@
sprintf -> snprintf
str{cat,cpy} -> strl{cat,cpy}

http://marc.theaimsgroup.com/?l=bugtraq&m=105638591907836&w=2

ok naddy@@
@
